section.container-color--dark-alt style=("background-color: #23272C")
  .container-image--center(data-interchange="[/public/icons/inlined/art/platform-tech-bg.svg, small]")
    section.section-article
      .row.align-center
        .columns.small-12
          .row.align-center
            .columns.small-12.medium-8
              h1.headline-2.text-center Platform Technology
              p.text-center.group See how the Platform works, the technology involved, and what it means to be HITRUST CSF certified on top of cloud providers like AWS and Azure.
          .row.row--card-grid
            .columns.small-12.medium-12.large-4
              .card.drop.container-color--gray-light
                img src="https://images.contentful.com/189dvqdsjh46/6ydXBtXKRU2Yu0mmsgYCcY/a16c46029da27d0b379fcc69fad5b05b/layer-infra.png" alt="Infrastructure Layer" class="soft-border"
                .card-section
                  p.lead.text-center <strong>Infrastructure Layer</strong>
                  p AWS and Azure provide VPCs, which cover a portion of compliance and security requirements.
                  p Within a VPC, the Datica Platform is installed. Everything within the Platform is strictly managed in adherence to Datica policies. The Platform uses a combination of Kubernetes and proprietary technology to orchestrate all DevOps duties for customers.
            .columns.small-12.medium-12.large-4
              .card.drop.container-color--gray-light
                img src="https://images.contentful.com/189dvqdsjh46/5cUz9cCIPSCag0CiQi44u4/b450448536c2d754573266b59bd8ea7d/layer-platform.png" alt="Platform Layer" class="soft-border"
                .card-section
                  p.lead.text-center <strong>Platform Layer</strong>
                  p Customers create an account within the Datica Platform. It is through the account that they gain access to HIPAA-eligible AWS Primitives or Azure Services, which are strictly controlled by the Platform.
                  p Within a customer account, the Platform containerizes all technology required to meet compliance controls from HIPAA, HITRUST, GDPR, and GxP. Things like logging, intrusion detection, and penetration testing, to name a few.
            .columns.small-12.medium-12.large-4
              .card.drop.container-color--gray-light
                img src="https://images.contentful.com/189dvqdsjh46/6bDMG7j3VYuoYkwEK4OkC2/5fcb3139b6401fbd1262f5f4285fc3a6/layer-app.png" alt="Application Layer" class="soft-border"
                .card-section
                  p.lead.text-center <strong>Application Layer</strong>
                  p Customers deploy their applications to containerized environments. They can have multiple environments within their Datica account, managing any type of technical use case.
                  p Administration of AWS Primitives or Azure Services are no longer required. Instead, customers simply allocate RAM to individual containers. Datica takes care of the rest.
                  p Deployment is done either through a <code>git push</code> buildpack-based process or by pushing custom Docker containers.

      .row.align-center
